        </h1>
        <p class="mb-6 text-base text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          As a Front-End Developer with 5 years of experience, I specialize in building intuitive and visually appealing user interfaces.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-2 dark:text-neutral-200 title-skill">
          The skills,tools and technologies I use
        </p>

        <div class="mt-7">

        <img src="/assets/images/logo-c.png" class="relative z-30 w-full rounded-xl tool-logo" />

        
        </div>

        
        <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/preethi-kumar-56a759163/" class="inline-flex gap-2 w-auto px-4 py-2 mt-10 text-xs font-semibold duration-300 ease-out border rounded-full bg-neutral-900 dark:bg-white dark:text-neutral-900 text-neutral-100 hover:border-neutral-700 border-neutral-900 dark:hover:border-neutral-300 hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-black dark:hover:text-white hover:text-neutral-900">
